title: RTD docs build has been failing since Aug 2 2025
body:
Read the Docs builds have been failing since 82ad62cfed5293e377984c1783c8367aed9fd4ed ([build](https://app.readthedocs.org/projects/mypy/builds/29068326/)).

The "latest" docs are still at the previous commit, e8147f2bdcd8899109fe1a9cffc770c436de95dc: https://mypy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

Build history: https://app.readthedocs.org/projects/mypy/builds/
